bookings.name: Linda
bookings.placeDescription: Pantai Tiga Warna (Three Colors Beach) by light boat which took 15 minutes to get there.The beach is under control of local Forestry Administration which has strict rules in order to keep the beach clean and tidy. Leaving any garbage in the beach would be subject to penalty.

places.name: Purwodadi Botanical Garden
places.description: Purwodadi Botanical Garden is a research centre in Purwodadi, Pasuruan, East Java, Indonesia. It has an area of 85 hectares and more than 10,000 types of trees and many plant collections. Callus cultures of Agave amaniensis by Setia Dewi were taken in 1988

places.name: Nganteb Beach
places.description: Ngantep Beach is located in Sukorejo Hamlet, Tumpakrejo Village, Gedangan District, Malang Regency, East Java. This beach is managed by Perhutani and the community around Ngantep Beach. The road to Ngantep Beach is quite easy to get through by private vehicle.

places.name: Coban Rondo waterfall
places.description: Coban Rondo waterfall is a beautiful water fall on the slope of Mount Panderman resort that is about 32 km to the west from Malang, it is very interesting to see and visit.The height of waterfall is about 60 meter.
